All-resp-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ {P : Pred A p} ‚Üí P Respects _‚âà_ ‚Üí (All P) Respects _‚Ü≠_
All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (refl xs‚âãys)   pxs             = All-resp-‚âã resp xs‚âãys pxs
All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (prep x‚âày p)   (px ‚à∑ pxs)      = resp x‚âày px ‚à∑ All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p pxs
All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (swap ‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚âà‚ÇÇ p) (px ‚à∑ py ‚à∑ pxs) = resp ‚âà‚ÇÇ py ‚à∑ resp ‚âà‚ÇÅ px ‚à∑ All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p pxs
All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (trans p‚ÇÅ p‚ÇÇ)  pxs             = All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p‚ÇÇ (All-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p‚ÇÅ pxs)
 
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ {P : Pred A p} ‚Üí P Respects _‚âà_ ‚Üí (Any P) Respects _‚Ü≠_
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (refl xs‚âãys) pxs                 = Any-resp-‚âã resp xs‚âãys pxs
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (prep x‚âày p) (here px)           = here (resp x‚âày px)
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (prep x‚âày p) (there pxs)         = there (Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p pxs)
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (swap x y p) (here px)           = there (here (resp x px))
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (swap x y p) (there (here px))   = here (resp y px)
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (swap x y p) (there (there pxs)) = there (there (Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p pxs))
Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp (trans p‚ÇÅ p‚ÇÇ) pxs                = Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p‚ÇÇ (Any-resp-‚Ü≠ resp p‚ÇÅ pxs)
 
AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ {R : Rel A r} ‚Üí Symmetric R ‚Üí R Respects‚ÇÇ _‚âà_ ‚Üí (AllPairs R) Respects _‚Ü≠_
AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp (refl xs‚âãys)     pxs             = AllPairs-resp-‚âã resp xs‚âãys pxs
AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp (prep x‚âày p)     (‚àº ‚à∑ pxs)       =
  All-resp-‚Ü≠ (proj‚ÇÅ resp) p (All.map (proj‚ÇÇ resp x‚âày) ‚àº) ‚à∑
  AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp p pxs
AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp@(r ≥ , rÀ°) (swap eq‚ÇÅ eq‚ÇÇ p) ((‚àº‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚àº‚ÇÇ) ‚à∑ ‚àº‚ÇÉ ‚à∑ pxs) =
  (sym (r ≥ eq‚ÇÇ (rÀ° eq‚ÇÅ ‚àº‚ÇÅ)) ‚à∑ All-resp-‚Ü≠ r ≥ p (All.map (rÀ° eq‚ÇÇ) ‚àº‚ÇÉ)) ‚à∑
  All-resp-‚Ü≠ r ≥ p (All.map (rÀ° eq‚ÇÅ) ‚àº‚ÇÇ) ‚à∑
  AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp p pxs
AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp (trans p‚ÇÅ p‚ÇÇ)    pxs             =
  AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp p‚ÇÇ (AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ sym resp p‚ÇÅ pxs)
 
‚àà-resp-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ {x} ‚Üí (x ‚àà_) Respects _‚Ü≠_
‚àà-resp-‚Ü≠ = Any-resp-‚Ü≠ (flip ‚âà-trans)
 
Unique-resp-‚Ü≠ : Unique Respects _‚Ü≠_
Unique-resp-‚Ü≠ = AllPairs-resp-‚Ü≠ (_‚àò ‚âà-sym) ‚ââ-resp‚ÇÇ

‚âã‚áí‚Ü≠ : _‚âã_ ‚áí _‚Ü≠_
‚âã‚áí‚Ü≠ = refl
 
‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã : _‚Ü≠_ Respects ≥ _‚âã_
‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys               (refl zs‚âãxs)         = refl (‚âã-trans zs‚âãxs xs‚âãys)
‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã (x‚âày ‚à∑ xs‚âãys)       (prep eq zs‚Ü≠xs)      = prep (‚âà-trans eq x‚âày) (‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs)
‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã (x‚âày ‚à∑ w‚âàz ‚à∑ xs‚âãys) (swap eq‚ÇÅ eq‚ÇÇ zs‚Ü≠xs) = swap (‚âà-trans eq‚ÇÅ w‚âàz) (‚âà-trans eq‚ÇÇ x‚âày) (‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs)
‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys               (trans ws‚Ü≠zs zs‚Ü≠xs)  = trans ws‚Ü≠zs (‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs)
 
‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã : _‚Ü≠_ RespectsÀ° _‚âã_
‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã xs‚âãys               (refl ys‚âãzs)         = refl (‚âã-trans (‚âã-sym xs‚âãys) ys‚âãzs)
‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã (x‚âày ‚à∑ xs‚âãys)       (prep eq zs‚Ü≠xs)      = prep (‚âà-trans (‚âà-sym x‚âày) eq) (‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs)
‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã (x‚âày ‚à∑ w‚âàz ‚à∑ xs‚âãys) (swap eq‚ÇÅ eq‚ÇÇ zs‚Ü≠xs) = swap (‚âà-trans (‚âà-sym x‚âày) eq‚ÇÅ) (‚âà-trans (‚âà-sym w‚âàz) eq‚ÇÇ) (‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs)
‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã xs‚âãys               (trans ws‚Ü≠zs zs‚Ü≠xs)  = trans (‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã xs‚âãys ws‚Ü≠zs) zs‚Ü≠xs

0<steps : ‚àÄ {xs ys} (xs‚Ü≠ys : xs ‚Ü≠ ys) ‚Üí 0 < steps xs‚Ü≠ys
0<steps (refl _)             = z<s
0<steps (prep eq xs‚Ü≠ys)      = m<n‚áím<1+n (0<steps xs‚Ü≠ys)
0<steps (swap eq‚ÇÅ eq‚ÇÇ xs‚Ü≠ys) = m<n‚áím<1+n (0<steps xs‚Ü≠ys)
0<steps (trans xs‚Ü≠ys xs‚Ü≠ys‚ÇÅ) =
  <-‚â§-trans (0<steps xs‚Ü≠ys) (m‚â§m+n (steps xs‚Ü≠ys) (steps xs‚Ü≠ys‚ÇÅ))
 
steps-respÀ° : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs} (ys‚âãxs : ys ‚âã xs) (ys‚Ü≠zs : ys ‚Ü≠ zs) ‚Üí
              steps (‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠zs) ‚â° steps ys‚Ü≠zs
steps-respÀ° _               (refl _)            = refl
steps-respÀ° (_ ‚à∑ ys‚âãxs)     (prep _ ys‚Ü≠zs)      = cong suc (steps-respÀ° ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠zs)
steps-respÀ° (_ ‚à∑ _ ‚à∑ ys‚âãxs) (swap _ _ ys‚Ü≠zs)    = cong suc (steps-respÀ° ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠zs)
steps-respÀ° ys‚âãxs           (trans ys‚Ü≠ws ws‚Ü≠zs) = cong (_+ steps ws‚Ü≠zs) (steps-respÀ° ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠ws)
 
steps-resp ≥ : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs} (xs‚âãys : xs ‚âã ys) (zs‚Ü≠xs : zs ‚Ü≠ xs) ‚Üí
              steps (‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã xs‚âãys zs‚Ü≠xs) ‚â° steps zs‚Ü≠xs
steps-resp ≥ _               (refl _)            = refl
steps-resp ≥ (_ ‚à∑ ys‚âãxs)     (prep _ ys‚Ü≠zs)      = cong suc (steps-resp ≥ ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠zs)
steps-resp ≥ (_ ‚à∑ _ ‚à∑ ys‚âãxs) (swap _ _ ys‚Ü≠zs)    = cong suc (steps-resp ≥ ys‚âãxs ys‚Ü≠zs)
steps-resp ≥ ys‚âãxs           (trans ys‚Ü≠ws ws‚Ü≠zs) = cong (steps ys‚Ü≠ws +_) (steps-resp ≥ ys‚âãxs ws‚Ü≠zs)

module _ {‚Ñì} (T : Setoid b ‚Ñì) where
 
  open Setoid T using () renaming (_‚âà_ to _‚âà‚Ä≤_)
  open Permutation T using () renaming (_‚Ü≠_ to _‚Ü≠‚Ä≤_)
 
  map‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {f} ‚Üí f Preserves _‚âà_ ‚ü∂ _‚âà‚Ä≤_ ‚Üí
         ‚àÄ {xs ys} ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí map f xs ‚Ü≠‚Ä≤ map f ys
  map‚Å∫ pres (refl xs‚âãys)  = refl (Pointwise.map‚Å∫ _ _ (Pointwise.map pres xs‚âãys))
  map‚Å∫ pres (prep x p)    = prep (pres x) (map‚Å∫ pres p)
  map‚Å∫ pres (swap x y p)  = swap (pres x) (pres y) (map‚Å∫ pres p)
  map‚Å∫ pres (trans p‚ÇÅ p‚ÇÇ) = trans (map‚Å∫ pres p‚ÇÅ) (map‚Å∫ pres p‚ÇÇ)

-- _++_
 
shift : ‚àÄ {v w} ‚Üí v ‚âà w ‚Üí (xs ys : List A) ‚Üí xs ++ [ v ] ++ ys ‚Ü≠ w ‚à∑ xs ++ ys
shift {v} {w} v‚âàw []       ys = prep v‚âàw ‚Ü≠-refl
shift {v} {w} v‚âàw (x ‚à∑ xs) ys = begin
  x ‚à∑ (xs ++ [ v ] ++ ys) <‚ü® shift v‚âàw xs ys ‚ü©
  x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs ++ ys        <<‚ü® ‚Ü≠-refl ‚ü©
  w ‚à∑ x ‚à∑ xs ++ ys        ‚àé
 
‚Ü≠-shift : ‚àÄ {v} (xs ys : List A) ‚Üí xs ++ [ v ] ++ ys ‚Ü≠ v ‚à∑ xs ++ ys
‚Ü≠-shift = shift ‚âà-refl
 
++‚Å∫À° : ‚àÄ xs {ys zs : List A} ‚Üí ys ‚Ü≠ zs ‚Üí xs ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ zs
++‚Å∫À° []       ys‚Ü≠zs = ys‚Ü≠zs
++‚Å∫À° (x ‚à∑ xs) ys‚Ü≠zs = ‚Ü≠-prep _ (++‚Å∫À° xs ys‚Ü≠zs)
 
++‚Å∫ ≥ : ‚àÄ {xs ys : List A} zs ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí xs ++ zs ‚Ü≠ ys ++ zs
++‚Å∫ ≥ zs (refl xs‚âãys)  = refl (Pointwise.++‚Å∫ xs‚âãys ‚âã-refl)
++‚Å∫ ≥ zs (prep x ‚Ü≠)    = prep x (++‚Å∫ ≥ zs ‚Ü≠)
++‚Å∫ ≥ zs (swap x y ‚Ü≠)  = swap x y (++‚Å∫ ≥ zs ‚Ü≠)
++‚Å∫ ≥ zs (trans ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ) = trans (++‚Å∫ ≥ zs ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ) (++‚Å∫ ≥ zs ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ)
 
++‚Å∫ : _++_ Preserves‚ÇÇ _‚Ü≠_ ‚ü∂ _‚Ü≠_ ‚ü∂ _‚Ü≠_
++‚Å∫ ws‚Ü≠xs ys‚Ü≠zs = trans (++‚Å∫ ≥ _ ws‚Ü≠xs) (++‚Å∫À° _ ys‚Ü≠zs)
 
-- Algebraic properties
 
++-identityÀ° : LeftIdentity _‚Ü≠_ [] _++_
++-identityÀ° xs = ‚Ü≠-refl
 
++-identity ≥ : RightIdentity _‚Ü≠_ [] _++_
++-identity ≥ xs = ‚Ü≠-reflexive (L‚Çö.++-identity ≥ xs)
 
++-identity : Identity _‚Ü≠_ [] _++_
++-identity = ++-identityÀ° , ++-identity ≥
 
++-assoc : Associative _‚Ü≠_ _++_
++-assoc xs ys zs = ‚Ü≠-reflexive (L‚Çö.++-assoc xs ys zs)
 
++-comm : Commutative _‚Ü≠_ _++_
++-comm []       ys = ‚Ü≠-sym (++-identity ≥ ys)
++-comm (x ‚à∑ xs) ys = begin
  x ‚à∑ xs ++ ys   <‚ü® ++-comm xs ys ‚ü©
  x ‚à∑ ys ++ xs   ‚Ü≠‚ü® ‚Ü≠-shift ys xs ‚ü®
  ys ++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚àé
 
-- Structures
 
++-isMagma : IsMagma _‚Ü≠_ _++_
++-isMagma = record
  { isEquivalence = ‚Ü≠-isEquivalence
  ; ‚àô-cong        = ++‚Å∫
  }
 
++-isSemigroup : IsSemigroup _‚Ü≠_ _++_
++-isSemigroup = record
  { isMagma = ++-isMagma
  ; assoc   = ++-assoc
  }
 
++-isMonoid : IsMonoid _‚Ü≠_ _++_ []
++-isMonoid = record
  { isSemigroup = ++-isSemigroup
  ; identity    = ++-identity
  }
 
++-isCommutativeMonoid : IsCommutativeMonoid _‚Ü≠_ _++_ []
++-isCommutativeMonoid = record
  { isMonoid = ++-isMonoid
  ; comm     = ++-comm
  }
 
-- Bundles
 
++-magma : Magma a (a ‚äî ‚Ñì)
++-magma = record
  { isMagma = ++-isMagma
  }
 
++-semigroup : Semigroup a (a ‚äî ‚Ñì)
++-semigroup = record
  { isSemigroup = ++-isSemigroup
  }
 
++-monoid : Monoid a (a ‚äî ‚Ñì)
++-monoid = record
  { isMonoid = ++-isMonoid
  }
 
++-commutativeMonoid : CommutativeMonoid a (a ‚äî ‚Ñì)
++-commutativeMonoid = record
  { isCommutativeMonoid = ++-isCommutativeMonoid
  }
 
-- Some other useful lemmas
 
zoom : ‚àÄ h {t xs ys : List A} ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí h ++ xs ++ t ‚Ü≠ h ++ ys ++ t
zoom h {t} = ++‚Å∫À° h ‚àò ++‚Å∫ ≥ t
 
inject : ‚àÄ (v : A) {ws xs ys zs} ‚Üí ws ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ zs ‚Üí
         ws ++ [ v ] ++ xs ‚Ü≠ ys ++ [ v ] ++ zs
inject v ws‚Ü≠ys xs‚Ü≠zs = trans (++‚Å∫À° _ (‚Ü≠-prep _ xs‚Ü≠zs)) (++‚Å∫ ≥ _ ws‚Ü≠ys)
 
shifts : ‚àÄ xs ys {zs : List A} ‚Üí xs ++ ys ++ zs ‚Ü≠ ys ++ xs ++ zs
shifts xs ys {zs} = begin
   xs ++ ys  ++ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® ++-assoc xs ys zs ‚ü®
  (xs ++ ys) ++ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® ++‚Å∫ ≥ zs (++-comm xs ys) ‚ü©
  (ys ++ xs) ++ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® ++-assoc ys xs zs ‚ü©
   ys ++ xs  ++ zs ‚àé
 
dropMiddleElement-‚âã : ‚àÄ {x} ws xs {ys} {zs} ‚Üí
           ws ++ [ x ] ++ ys ‚âã xs ++ [ x ] ++ zs ‚Üí
           ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ zs
dropMiddleElement-‚âã []       []       (_   ‚à∑ eq) = ‚âã‚áí‚Ü≠ eq
dropMiddleElement-‚âã []       (x ‚à∑ xs) (w‚âàv ‚à∑ eq) = ‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã (‚âã-sym eq) (shift w‚âàv xs _)
dropMiddleElement-‚âã (w ‚à∑ ws) []       (w‚âàx ‚à∑ eq) = ‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã eq (‚Ü≠-sym (shift (‚âà-sym w‚âàx) ws _))
dropMiddleElement-‚âã (w ‚à∑ ws) (x ‚à∑ xs) (w‚âàx ‚à∑ eq) = prep w‚âàx (dropMiddleElement-‚âã ws xs eq)
 
dropMiddleElement : ‚àÄ {v} ws xs {ys zs} ‚Üí
                    ws ++ [ v ] ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ [ v ] ++ zs ‚Üí
                    ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ zs
dropMiddleElement {v} ws xs {ys} {zs} p = helper p ws xs ‚âã-refl ‚âã-refl
  where
  lemma : ‚àÄ {w x y z} ‚Üí w ‚âà x ‚Üí x ‚âà y ‚Üí z ‚âà y ‚Üí w ‚âà z
  lemma w‚âàx x‚âày z‚âày = ‚âà-trans (‚âà-trans w‚âàx x‚âày) (‚âà-sym z‚âày)
 
  open PermutationReasoning
 
  -- The l‚Ä≤ & l‚Ä≥ could be eliminated at the cost of making the `trans` case
  -- much more difficult to prove. At the very least would require using `Acc`.
  helper : ‚àÄ {l‚Ä≤ l‚Ä≥ : List A} ‚Üí l‚Ä≤ ‚Ü≠ l‚Ä≥ ‚Üí
           ‚àÄ ws xs {ys zs : List A} ‚Üí
           ws ++ [ v ] ++ ys ‚âã l‚Ä≤ ‚Üí
           xs ++ [ v ] ++ zs ‚âã l‚Ä≥ ‚Üí
           ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ zs
  helper {as}     {bs}     (refl eq3) ws xs {ys} {zs} eq1 eq2 =
    dropMiddleElement-‚âã ws xs (‚âã-trans (‚âã-trans eq1 eq3) (‚âã-sym eq2))
  helper {_ ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ bs} (prep _ as‚Ü≠bs) [] [] {ys} {zs} (_ ‚à∑ ys‚âãas) (_ ‚à∑ zs‚âãbs) = begin
    ys               ‚âã‚ü®  ys‚âãas ‚ü©
    as               ‚Ü≠‚ü®  as‚Ü≠bs ‚ü©
    bs               ‚âã‚ü® zs‚âãbs ‚ü®
    zs               ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ bs} (prep a‚âàb as‚Ü≠bs) [] (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    ys               ‚âã‚ü®  ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    as               ‚Ü≠‚ü®  as‚Ü≠bs ‚ü©
    bs               ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü®
    xs ++ v ‚à∑ zs     ‚Ü≠‚ü®  shift (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÅ a‚âàb ‚âà‚ÇÇ) xs zs ‚ü©
    x ‚à∑ xs ++ zs     ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ bs} (prep v‚âàw p) (w ‚à∑ ws) [] {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    w ‚à∑ ws ++ ys     ‚Ü≠‚ü®  ‚Ü≠-sym (shift (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÇ (‚âà-sym v‚âàw) ‚âà‚ÇÅ) ws ys) ‚ü©
    ws ++ v ‚à∑ ys     ‚âã‚ü®  ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    as               ‚Ü≠‚ü®  p ‚ü©
    bs               ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü®
    zs               ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ bs} (prep w‚âàx p) (w ‚à∑ ws) (x ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    w ‚à∑ ws ++ ys     ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÅ w‚âàx ‚âà‚ÇÇ) (helper p ws xs ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) ‚ü©
    x ‚à∑ xs ++ zs     ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap v‚âàx y‚âàv p) [] [] {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    ys               ‚âã‚ü®  ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    a ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü®  prep (‚âà-trans (‚âà-trans (‚âà-trans y‚âàv (‚âà-sym ‚âà‚ÇÇ)) ‚âà‚ÇÅ) v‚âàx) p ‚ü©
    b ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü®
    zs               ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap v‚âàw y‚âàw p) [] (x ‚à∑ []) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    ys               ‚âã‚ü®  ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    a ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü®  prep y‚âàw p ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü®
    x ‚à∑ zs           ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap v‚âàw y‚âàx p) [] (x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    ys               ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    a ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep y‚âàx p ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÇ) ‚ü©
    x ‚à∑ xs ++ v ‚à∑ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep ‚âà-refl (shift (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÅ v‚âàw (head ‚âã‚ÇÇ)) xs zs) ‚ü©
    x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs ++ zs ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap w‚âàx _ p) (w ‚à∑ []) [] {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    w ‚à∑ ys           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ tail (‚âã‚ÇÅ) ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep w‚âàx p ‚ü©
    b ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü©
    zs               ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap w‚âày x‚âàv p) (w ‚à∑ x ‚à∑ ws) [] {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    w ‚à∑ x ‚à∑ ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep ‚âà-refl (‚Ü≠-sym (shift (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÇ (‚âà-sym x‚âàv) (head ‚âã‚ÇÅ)) ws ys)) ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ ws ++ v ‚à∑ ys ‚âã‚ü® ‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep w‚âày p ‚ü©
    b ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü©
    zs               ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap x‚âàv v‚âày p) (x ‚à∑ []) (y ‚à∑ []) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    x ‚à∑ ys           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep (‚âà-trans x‚âàv (‚âà-trans (‚âà-sym (head ‚âã‚ÇÇ)) (‚âà-trans (head ‚âã‚ÇÅ) v‚âày))) p ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÇ) ‚ü©
    y ‚à∑ zs           ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap y‚âàw v‚âàz p) (y ‚à∑ []) (z ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    y ‚à∑ ys           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep y‚âàw p ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym ‚âã‚ÇÇ ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ xs ++ v ‚à∑ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® ‚Ü≠-prep w (‚Ü≠-shift xs zs) ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ v ‚à∑ xs ++ zs ‚Ü≠‚ü® swap ‚âà-refl (lemma (head ‚âã‚ÇÅ) v‚âàz ‚âà‚ÇÇ) ‚Ü≠-refl ‚ü©
    z ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs ++ zs ‚àé
  helper {_ ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ as} {_ ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ bs} (swap y‚âàv w‚âàz p) (y ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ ws) (z ‚à∑ []) {ys} {zs}    (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    y ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠‚ü® swap (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÅ y‚âàv (head ‚âã‚ÇÇ)) ‚âà-refl ‚Ü≠-refl ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ v ‚à∑ ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠‚ü® ‚Ü≠-prep w (‚Ü≠-sym (‚Ü≠-shift ws ys)) ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ ws ++ v ‚à∑ ys ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ as           ‚Ü≠‚ü® prep w‚âàz p ‚ü©
    _ ‚à∑ bs           ‚âã‚ü® ‚âã-sym (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ tail ‚âã‚ÇÇ) ‚ü©
    z ‚à∑ zs           ‚àé
  helper (swap x‚âàz y‚âàw p) (x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ ws) (w ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ xs) {ys} {zs} (‚âà‚ÇÅ ‚à∑ ‚âà‚ÇÉ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÅ) (‚âà‚ÇÇ ‚à∑ ‚âà‚ÇÑ ‚à∑ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) = begin
    x ‚à∑ y ‚à∑ ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠‚ü® swap (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÅ x‚âàz ‚âà‚ÇÑ) (lemma ‚âà‚ÇÉ y‚âàw ‚âà‚ÇÇ) (helper p ws xs ‚âã‚ÇÅ ‚âã‚ÇÇ) ‚ü©
    w ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ xs ++ zs ‚àé
  helper {as} {bs} (trans p‚ÇÅ p‚ÇÇ) ws xs eq1 eq2
    with ‚àà-‚àÉ++ S (‚àà-resp-‚Ü≠ (‚Ü≠-respÀ°-‚âã (‚âã-sym eq1) p‚ÇÅ) (‚àà-insert S ws ‚âà-refl))
  ... | (h , t , w , v‚âàw , eq) = trans
    (helper p‚ÇÅ ws h eq1 (‚âã-trans (‚âã.++‚Å∫ ‚âã-refl (v‚âàw ‚à∑ ‚âã-refl)) (‚âã-sym eq)))
    (helper p‚ÇÇ h xs (‚âã-trans (‚âã.++‚Å∫ ‚âã-refl (v‚âàw ‚à∑ ‚âã-refl)) (‚âã-sym eq)) eq2)
 
dropMiddle : ‚àÄ {vs} ws xs {ys zs} ‚Üí
             ws ++ vs ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ vs ++ zs ‚Üí
             ws ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ zs
dropMiddle {[]}     ws xs p = p
dropMiddle {v ‚à∑ vs} ws xs p = dropMiddle ws xs (dropMiddleElement ws xs p)
 
split : ‚àÄ (v : A) as bs {xs} ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ as ++ [ v ] ++ bs ‚Üí ‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª ps qs ‚Üí xs ‚âã ps ++ [ v ] ++ qs
split v as bs p = helper as bs p (<-wellFounded (steps p))
  where
  helper : ‚àÄ as bs {xs} (p : xs ‚Ü≠ as ++ [ v ] ++ bs) ‚Üí Acc _<_ (steps p) ‚Üí
           ‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª ps qs ‚Üí xs ‚âã ps ++ [ v ] ++ qs
  helper []           bs (refl eq)    _ = []         , bs , eq
  helper (a ‚à∑ [])     bs (refl eq)    _ = [ a ]      , bs , eq
  helper (a ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ as) bs (refl eq)    _ = a ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ as , bs , eq
  helper []           bs (prep v‚âàx _) _ = [] , _ , v‚âàx ‚à∑ ‚âã-refl
  helper (a ‚à∑ as)     bs (prep eq as‚Ü≠xs) (acc rec) with helper as bs as‚Ü≠xs (rec ‚â§-refl)
  ... | (ps , qs , eq‚ÇÇ) = a ‚à∑ ps , qs , eq ‚à∑ eq‚ÇÇ
  helper [] (b ‚à∑ bs)     (swap x‚âàb y‚âàv _) _ = [ b ] , _     , x‚âàb ‚à∑ y‚âàv ‚à∑ ‚âã-refl
  helper (a ‚à∑ [])     bs (swap x‚âàv y‚âàa ‚Ü≠) _ = []    , a ‚à∑ _ , x‚âàv ‚à∑ y‚âàa ‚à∑ ‚âã-refl
  helper (a ‚à∑ b ‚à∑ as) bs (swap x‚âàb y‚âàa as‚Ü≠xs) (acc rec) with helper as bs as‚Ü≠xs (rec ‚â§-refl)
  ... | (ps , qs , eq) = b ‚à∑ a ‚à∑ ps , qs , x‚âàb ‚à∑ y‚âàa ‚à∑ eq
  helper as           bs (trans ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ) (acc rec) with helper as bs ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ (rec (m<n+m (steps ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ) (0<steps ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ)))
  ... | (ps , qs , eq) = helper ps qs (‚Ü≠-resp ≥-‚âã eq ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ)
      (rec (subst (_< _) (sym (steps-resp ≥ eq ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ)) (m<m+n (steps ‚Ü≠‚ÇÅ) (0<steps ‚Ü≠‚ÇÇ))))

-- filter
 
module _ {p} {P : Pred A p} (P? : Decidable P) (P‚âà : P Respects _‚âà_) where
 
  filter‚Å∫ : ‚àÄ {xs ys : List A} ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí filter P? xs ‚Ü≠ filter P? ys
  filter‚Å∫ (refl xs‚âãys)        = refl (‚âã.filter‚Å∫ P? P‚âà xs‚âãys)
  filter‚Å∫ (trans xs‚Ü≠zs zs‚Ü≠ys) = trans (filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠zs) (filter‚Å∫ zs‚Ü≠ys)
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ ys} (prep x‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) with P? x | P? y
  ... | yes _  | yes _  = prep x‚âày (filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys)
  ... | yes Px | no ¬¨Py = contradiction (P‚âà x‚âày Px) ¬¨Py
  ... | no ¬¨Px | yes Py = contradiction (P‚âà (‚âà-sym x‚âày) Py) ¬¨Px
  ... | no  _  | no  _  = filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ ys} (swap x‚âàz w‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) with P? x | P? y
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ ys} (swap x‚âàz w‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) | no ¬¨Px | no ¬¨Py
    with P? z | P? w
  ... | _      | yes Pw = contradiction (P‚âà w‚âày Pw) ¬¨Py
  ... | yes Pz | _      = contradiction (P‚âà (‚âà-sym x‚âàz) Pz) ¬¨Px
  ... | no _   | no  _  = filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ ys} (swap x‚âàz w‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) | no ¬¨Px | yes Py
    with P? z | P? w
  ... | _      | no ¬¨Pw = contradiction (P‚âà (‚âà-sym w‚âày) Py) ¬¨Pw
  ... | yes Pz | _      = contradiction (P‚âà (‚âà-sym x‚âàz) Pz) ¬¨Px
  ... | no _   | yes _  = prep w‚âày (filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys)
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ ys} (swap x‚âàz w‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys)  | yes Px | no ¬¨Py
    with P? z | P? w
  ... | no ¬¨Pz | _      = contradiction (P‚âà x‚âàz Px) ¬¨Pz
  ... | _      | yes Pw = contradiction (P‚âà w‚âày Pw) ¬¨Py
  ... | yes _  | no _   = prep x‚âàz (filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys)
  filter‚Å∫ {x ‚à∑ w ‚à∑ xs} {y ‚à∑ z ‚à∑ ys} (swap x‚âàz w‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) | yes Px | yes Py
    with P? z | P? w
  ... | no ¬¨Pz | _      = contradiction (P‚âà x‚âàz Px) ¬¨Pz
  ... | _      | no ¬¨Pw = contradiction (P‚âà (‚âà-sym w‚âày) Py) ¬¨Pw
  ... | yes _  | yes _  = swap x‚âàz w‚âày (filter‚Å∫ xs‚Ü≠ys)

-- partition
 
module _ {p} {P : Pred A p} (P? : Decidable P) where
 
  partition-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ xs ‚Üí (let ys , zs = partition P? xs) ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ++ zs
  partition-‚Ü≠ []       = ‚Ü≠-refl
  partition-‚Ü≠ (x ‚à∑ xs) with does (P? x)
  ... | true  = ‚Ü≠-prep x (partition-‚Ü≠ xs)
  ... | false = ‚Ü≠-trans (‚Ü≠-prep x (partition-‚Ü≠ xs)) (‚Ü≠-sym (‚Ü≠-shift _ _))
    where open PermutationReasoning
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- merge
 
module _ {‚Ñì} {R : Rel A ‚Ñì} (R? : B.Decidable R) where
 
  merge-‚Ü≠ : ‚àÄ xs ys ‚Üí merge R? xs ys ‚Ü≠ xs ++ ys
  merge-‚Ü≠ []       []       = ‚Ü≠-refl
  merge-‚Ü≠ []       (y ‚à∑ ys) = ‚Ü≠-refl
  merge-‚Ü≠ (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = ‚Ü≠-sym (++-identity ≥ (x ‚à∑ xs))
  merge-‚Ü≠ (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys)
    with does (R? x y) | merge-‚Ü≠ xs (y ‚à∑ ys) | merge-‚Ü≠ (x ‚à∑ xs) ys
  ... | true  | rec | _   = ‚Ü≠-prep x rec
  ... | false | _   | rec = begin
    y ‚à∑ merge R? (x ‚à∑ xs) ys <‚ü® rec ‚ü©
    y ‚à∑ x ‚à∑ xs ++ ys         ‚Ü≠‚ü® ‚Ü≠-shift (x ‚à∑ xs) ys ‚ü®
    (x ‚à∑ xs) ++ y ‚à∑ ys       ‚â°‚ü® L‚Çö.++-assoc [ x ] xs (y ‚à∑ ys) ‚ü®
    x ‚à∑ xs ++ y ‚à∑ ys         ‚àé
    where open PermutationReasoning
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- _‚à∑ ≥_
 
‚à∑‚Ü≠‚à∑ ≥ : ‚àÄ (x : A) xs ‚Üí x ‚à∑ xs ‚Ü≠ xs ‚à∑ ≥ x
‚à∑‚Ü≠‚à∑ ≥ x xs = ‚Ü≠-sym (begin
  xs ++ [ x ]   ‚Ü≠‚ü® ‚Ü≠-shift xs [] ‚ü©
  x ‚à∑ xs ++ []  ‚â°‚ü® L‚Çö.++-identity ≥ _ ‚ü©
  x ‚à∑ xs        ‚àé)
  where open PermutationReasoning
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
--  ≥++
 
++‚Ü≠ ≥++ : ‚àÄ (xs ys : List A) ‚Üí xs ++ ys ‚Ü≠ xs  ≥++ ys
++‚Ü≠ ≥++ []       ys = ‚Ü≠-refl
++‚Ü≠ ≥++ (x ‚à∑ xs) ys = ‚Ü≠-trans (‚Ü≠-sym (‚Ü≠-shift xs ys)) (++‚Ü≠ ≥++ xs (x ‚à∑ ys))
 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- foldr of Commutative Monoid
 
module _ {_‚àô_ : Op‚ÇÇ A} {Œµ : A} (isCmonoid : IsCommutativeMonoid _‚âà_ _‚àô_ Œµ) where
  open module CM = IsCommutativeMonoid isCmonoid
 
  private
    module S = RelSetoid setoid
 
    cmonoid : CommutativeMonoid _ _
    cmonoid = record { isCommutativeMonoid = isCmonoid }
 
  open ACM cmonoid
 
  foldr-commMonoid : ‚àÄ {xs ys} ‚Üí xs ‚Ü≠ ys ‚Üí foldr _‚àô_ Œµ xs ‚âà foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys
  foldr-commMonoid (refl []) = CM.refl
  foldr-commMonoid (refl (x‚âày ‚à∑ xs‚âàys)) = ‚àô-cong x‚âày (foldr-commMonoid (Permutation.refl xs‚âàys))
  foldr-commMonoid (prep x‚âày xs‚Ü≠ys) = ‚àô-cong x‚âày (foldr-commMonoid xs‚Ü≠ys)
  foldr-commMonoid (swap {xs} {ys} {x} {y} {x‚Ä≤} {y‚Ä≤} x‚âàx‚Ä≤ y‚âày‚Ä≤ xs‚Ü≠ys) = S.begin
    x ‚àô (y ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ xs)   S.‚âà‚ü® ‚àô-congÀ° (‚àô-congÀ° (foldr-commMonoid xs‚Ü≠ys)) ‚ü©
    x ‚àô (y ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys)   S.‚âà‚ü® assoc x y (foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys) ‚ü®
    (x ‚àô y) ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys   S.‚âà‚ü® ‚àô-cong ≥ (comm x y) ‚ü©
    (y ‚àô x) ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys   S.‚âà‚ü® ‚àô-cong ≥ (‚àô-cong y‚âày‚Ä≤ x‚âàx‚Ä≤) ‚ü©
    (y‚Ä≤ ‚àô x‚Ä≤) ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys S.‚âà‚ü® assoc y‚Ä≤ x‚Ä≤ (foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys) ‚ü©
    y‚Ä≤ ‚àô (x‚Ä≤ ‚àô foldr _‚àô_ Œµ ys) S.‚àé
  foldr-commMonoid (trans xs‚Ü≠ys ys‚Ü≠zs) = CM.trans (foldr-commMonoid xs‚Ü≠ys) (foldr-commMonoid ys‚Ü≠zs)
